Output docs/demo/migrate.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 740
Set Height 400
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 55ms
Set Padding 24
Set CursorBlink false

Hide
Type "export HOME=/tmp/gnbd-migrate"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Show

Sleep 300ms
Type "cat ~/.zshrc"
Enter
Sleep 1.8s

Type "gnb migrate"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s

Type "y"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "gnb list"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s
